'''''Too Much of Me Is Magic''''' is a one round adventure module set in the [[Living City]] organized play program. It was published in 2001, and is intended for adventurers of 5{{th}}&ndash;13{{th}} levels.

{{quote|''The solar Aethylnmur requires the aid of Ravens Bluff's most accomplished heroes. This go-round, there won't be time
for a trip to the bakery.''}}

